data.description: ***AWESOME RENTAL POTENTIAL/INVESTMENT PROPERTY - VACATION SPOT***  PLUS, SPECTACULAR WATER VIEWS AND SOUTHERN BREEZES*** Views of KINGFISHER BEACH & MATAGORDA BAY FROM MASSIVE COVERED BACK PORCH!  Open concept 3 Bed, 2 Bath w/Center-island in kitchen and w/walk-in PANTRY/LAUNDRY ROOM! High ceilings with crown molding, "French" look back door, to covered porch, which runs length of residence.  Dining room adjacent to living and dining; traditional open concept. Tall bom-a-range shaped Bar/Island separates kitchen from living, dining areas. Tons of windows breath light into this open concept!  Huge walk-in master closet w/shower, even garden tub!  2 guest rooms share bath w/shower tub combo; great for guests, rentals! White picket style fenced around back yard w/scattered fruit trees.  Double 100 x 120 lot means you can build a whole 2nd hous! Or, add pool and just enjoy the view! Maybe even invite your friends w/their RV's!  3 residences allowed per POC W/S hook up!  Out building in back; great storage space for yard or fishing equipment! All you need in POC for family fun, and/or invesment!  Set up your VIEWING TODAY!
